{
  "stem": "868.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The war was nowhere near ending.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We lived mostly on various concoction made of chestnuts, which grew abundantly in those areas.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We cooked them, we broiled them, we chopped them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We did everything that was possible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We decided we would go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We went.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Our group was about eight, eight people, our family, three, and some others.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We traveled by train from where we were to Cuneo, from Cuneo to Torino, Turin, continuing all the time to what's Florence.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Somewhere between Genova and Florence, the train was suddenly stopped.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We heard sirens.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the train was suddenly stopped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We looked outside.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were in the middle of nowhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was no railroad station near us, nothing that indicated or justified a stop.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I looked out the windows, and I immediately saw that the entire train was surrounded by German soldiers with their arms at the ready, with their guns at, at the ready.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We knew that this is the end of the line.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were looking for Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And in effect, we saw, coming down one railroad car after another, a German officer accompanied by two [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] fascist guards, Italian, and an interpreter.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they picked people, here and there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Show us document, document.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When they came to us, a comedy kind of started.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We had no, no papers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went down to the nearest village, and I spoke to a young lady I had gotten to know on the various trips from where we were down to that small village, very, very small.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they had a grocery store there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And occasionally, they would allow us a little bit of sugar, a little bit of oil to--",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
